articles.title: Mayoral preliminary: Wu maintains huge lead over Kraft as both advance to November election
articles.description:
Wu and Kraft, predictably, will move on to the general election in November after the field narrowed Tuesday night.

The post Mayoral preliminary: Wu maintains huge lead over Kraft as both advance to November election appeared first on Boston.com.
summary: Wu and Kraft advance to the November mayoral election after Tuesday's preliminary results.
Wu maintains a significant lead over Kraft, indicating strong voter support.
Boston residents will choose between Wu's policies and Kraft's vision in the upcoming election.
